<h4 id="background">Background</h4>
<p>Game theory is the study of mathematical models of strategic interaction among rational decision-makers. It has applications in all fields of social science
, as well as in logic, systems science, and computer science.</p>

<h4 id="component">component</h4>
<ol>
  <li>player</li>
  <li>strategy  Notation s</li>
  <li>payoff    Notation u</li>
  <li>equilibrium</li>
</ol>

